definition: extra/surplus/remaining/remainder after division/(following numerical value) or more/in excess of (some number)/residue (math.)/after/I/me

sentences.english: But, you can perform range scans on the remaining columns in the index key.
sentences.chinese: 但是，您可以在索引键的其余列上执行范围扫面。

sentences.english: But others seem content to rely on automatic stabilisers.
sentences.chinese: 而其余国家则情愿依赖自动稳定器的作用。

sentences.english: Two passengers were hospitalized in critical condition, while injuries to the 11 others were less serious.
sentences.chinese: 两名乘客尚在抢救中，其余11名乘客伤势较轻。

sentences.english: This article provides the rest of the story.
sentences.chinese: 本文给出这个故事的其余部分。

sentences.english: For example, the meridian pertaining to the kidney is named the kidney meridian, and the rest may be deduced by analogy.
sentences.chinese: 例如，属于肾的经脉命名为肾经，其余由此类推。

sentences.english: As for the other resultant mental states that occur during the rest of life, they number thirty-two.
sentences.chinese: 在生命的其余时间生起的果报心共有三十二种。

sentences.english: Octagon —shapedturrets rest on the four corners of the wall.
sentences.chinese: 八角形塔楼其余的四个角落的墙上。

sentences.english: What follows is the rest of our conversation.
sentences.chinese: 以下是我们谈话的其余部分。

sentences.english: Ignoring those, the remaining central shape is nondescript.
sentences.chinese: 不顾这些，其余的中央形状是不伦不类。

sentences.english: All the rest of the Israelites were also of one mind to make David king.
sentences.chinese: 以色列其余的人也都一心要立大卫作王。

sentences.english: It will help us recover the rest of the animal more easily and efficiently.
sentences.chinese: 这将帮助我们更容易和有效得恢复其余的动物。

sentences.english: Most came from India and the rest hailed from 11 other countries.
sentences.chinese: 大部分成员来自印度，其余则来自其他11个国家。

sentences.english: One third of the pawpaw is for the dish, the remainder is for you.
sentences.chinese: 这个木瓜三分之一用来做菜，其余的都是你的啦。

sentences.english: About half of them are Chinese, and the rest are Americans from Chengdu's tightknit community of expatriates.
sentences.chinese: 当中大约一半是中国人，其余是生活在成都的美国人。

sentences.english: Except the normal control group, experimental colitis was induced in all mice by oxazolone enema.
sentences.chinese: 除正常对照组外，其余小鼠均以恶唑酮灌肠造模。

sentences.english: A: I have a tuition scholarship from the university. Otherwise I’m on my own.
sentences.chinese: 学校只让我免缴学费，其余还是自掏腰包。

definition: other/the others/else/other than it/in addition to the thing mentioned above
to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including
apart from/other than/except for/external/outside of/on the other side of/beyond
in large part/the greater part/the majority
